    },
    {
      "type": "custom_html",
      "html": "<header class=\"relative w-full min-h-[60vh] flex items-center bg-slate-50 overflow-hidden\">\n        <!-- Background Image -->\n        <img src=\"https://picsum.photos/seed/minimalist-office-space/1920/1080\" alt=\"Minimalist office environment\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" class=\"absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover object-center z-0 scale-105\">\n        \n        <!-- Gradient Overlay -->\n        <div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-r from-white via-white/95 to-white/60 z-10\"></div>\n\n        <div class=\"relative z-20 max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8 w-full py-20 mt-10\">\n            <div class=\"grid grid-cols-12 gap-8\">\n                <!-- Text Content -->\n                <div class=\"col-span-12 md:col-span-9 lg:col-span-8 flex flex-col justify-center\">\n                    <h1 class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-bold text-slate-900 tracking-tighter leading-[1.1] mb-6\">\n                        Navigating family transitions with <span class=\"text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-600 to-blue-400\">dignity and expertise.</span>\n                    </h1>\n                    \n                    <p class=\"text-lg md:text-xl text-slate-600 font-light leading-relaxed max-w-2xl\">\n                        With over four decades of family law experience in Texas, Steve Bruneman provides a neutral, structured, and empathetic environment to resolve complex disputes outside the courtroom.\n                    </p>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </header>"
    },
    {
      "type": "custom_html",
      "html": "<section class=\"py-32 bg-white relative overflow-hidden\">\n        <div class=\"max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8\">\n            <div class=\"grid grid-cols-12 gap-16 lg:gap-24 items-start\">\n                \n                <!-- Left: Portrait & Badges (5 cols) -->\n                <div class=\"col-span-12 lg:col-span-5 relative sticky top-32\">\n                    <div class=\"absolute -top-6 -left-6 w-full h-full bg-slate-50 rounded-3xl z-0 border border-slate-100\"></div>\n                    \n                    <div class=\"relative z-10 rounded-3xl overflow-hidden shadow-2xl shadow-slate-200/50 group\">\n                        <img src=\"https://picsum.photos/seed/steve-bruneman-portrait/800/1000\" alt=\"Steve Bruneman Portrait\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" class=\"w-full h-auto object-cover transform group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-700 ease-in-out\">\n                    </div>\n                    \n                    <!-- Floating Stat Badge -->\n                    <div class=\"absolute -bottom-8 right-8 z-20 bg-white p-6 rounded-2xl shadow-xl border border-slate-50\">\n                        <div class=\"flex items-center gap-4\">\n                            <div class=\"w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-blue-50 flex items-center justify-center\">\n                                <svg class=\"w-6 h-6 text-blue-600\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2\" d=\"M3 6l3 1m0 0l-3 9a5.002 5.002 0 006.001 0M6 7l3 9M6 7l6-2m6 2l3-1m-3 1l-3 9a5.002 5.002 0 006.001 0M18 7l3 9m-3-9l-6-2m0-2v2m0 16V5m0 16H9m3 0h3\"></path></svg>\n                            </div>\n                            <div>\n                                <p class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900\">40+</p>\n                                <p class=\"text-xs font-semibold text-slate-500 uppercase tracking-wider\">Years of Practice</p>\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n\n                <!-- Right: Content Narrative (7 cols) -->\n                <div class=\"col-span-12 lg:col-span-7 pt-8 lg:pt-0\">\n                    <h2 class=\"text-sm font-bold text-blue-600 uppercase tracking-widest mb-3\">The Mediator</h2>\n                    <h3 class=\"text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-slate-900 tracking-tight mb-8 leading-tight\">\n                        A career built on the front lines of family law litigation.\n                    </h3>\n                    \n                    <div class=\"space-y-6 text-slate-600 leading-relaxed text-lg font-light\">\n                        <p>\n                            Steve Bruneman began his legal career in 1982, quickly establishing himself as a formidable presence in Dallas family courts. For decades, he navigated the intense and often destructive waters of divorce litigation, representing clients in highly contentious custody battles and complex marital estate divisions.\n                        </p>\n                        <p>\n                            However, witnessing the profound emotional and financial devastation that trials inflict on families led to a pivot in his philosophy. While remaining a fierce advocate when necessary, Steve recognized that the courtroom is rarely the best place to restructure a family's future. \n                        </p>\n                        <p>\n                            Today, Steve dedicates his expertise exclusively to mediation. He leverages his extensive trial experience to offer parties a realistic assessment of their judicial alternatives. By understanding exactly how judges and juries react to specific facts, he helps parties move past entrenched positions toward equitable, self-determined settlements.\n                        </p>\n                        <p>\n                            His deep understanding of the psychological dynamics inherent in divorce—particularly concerning personality disorders, addiction, and high-conflict personalities—makes him uniquely equipped to manage volatile emotions and keep negotiations constructive.\n                        </p>\n                    </div>\n\n                    <div class=\"mt-12 pt-8 border-t border-slate-100\">\n                        <h4 class=\"font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-4\">Professional Affiliations &amp; Honors</h4>\n                        <ul class=\"space-y-3\">\n                            <li class=\"flex items-start\">\n                                <svg class=\"w-5 h-5 text-blue-500 mt-0.5 mr-3 flex-shrink-0\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2\" d=\"M5 13l4 4L19 7\"></path></svg>\n                                <span class=\"text-slate-600\">Board Certified in Family Law by the Texas Board of Legal Specialization (since 2000)</span>\n                            </li>\n                            <li class=\"flex items-start\">\n                                <svg class=\"w-5 h-5 text-blue-500 mt-0.5 mr-3 flex-shrink-0\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2\" d=\"M5 13l4 4L19 7\"></path></svg>\n                                <span class=\"text-slate-600\">AV Preeminent® Rated by Martindale-Hubbell®</span>\n                            </li>\n                            <li class=\"flex items-start\">\n                                <svg class=\"w-5 h-5 text-blue-500 mt-0.5 mr-3 flex-shrink-0\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2\" d=\"M5 13l4 4L19 7\"></path></svg>\n                                <span class=\"text-slate-600\">Selected to Texas Super Lawyers (Seven consecutive years)</span>\n                            </li>\n                            <li class=\"flex items-start\">\n                                <svg class=\"w-5 h-5 text-blue-500 mt-0.5 mr-3 flex-shrink-0\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2\" d=\"M5 13l4 4L19 7\"></path></svg>\n                                <span class=\"text-slate-600\">Author of <em>\"Winning the Marriage Gamble\"</em></span>\n                            </li>\n                        </ul>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>"
    },
    {
      "type": "custom_html",
      "html": "<section class=\"py-32 bg-slate-50\">\n        <div class=\"max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8\">\n            <div class=\"max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center mb-16\">\n                <h2 class=\"text-sm font-bold text-blue-600 uppercase tracking-widest mb-3\">Our Approach</h2>\n                <h3 class=\"text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-slate-900 tracking-tight\">\n                    Why choose Bruneman Mediations?\n                </h3>\n            </div>\n\n            <div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8\">\n                <!-- Point 1 -->\n                <div class=\"bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl border border-slate-100 shadow-xl shadow-slate-200/30\">\n                    <div class=\"w-10 h-10 rounded bg-blue-50 flex items-center justify-center mb-6\">\n                        <span class=\"text-blue-600 font-bold\">01</span>\n                    </div>\n                    <h4 class=\"text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3\">Reality-Tested Solutions</h4>\n                    <p class=\"text-slate-500 text-sm leading-relaxed\">\n                        We don't just facilitate conversation; we provide pragmatic reality checks. Drawing on decades of trial outcomes, we help parties understand the likely judicial alternatives to settlement, fostering more reasonable compromises.\n                    </p>\n                </div>\n\n                <!-- Point 2 -->\n                <div class=\"bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl border border-slate-100 shadow-xl shadow-slate-200/30\">\n                    <div class=\"w-10 h-10 rounded bg-blue-50 flex items-center justify-center mb-6\">\n                        <span class=\"text-blue-600 font-bold\">02</span>\n                    </div>\n                    <h4 class=\"text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3\">Emotional De-escalation</h4>\n                    <p class=\"text-slate-500 text-sm leading-relaxed\">\n                        Divorce is inherently emotional. Our structured mediation environments are designed to reduce volatility, separate the personal animosity from the legal issues, and keep the focus squarely on future stability.\n                    </p>\n                </div>\n\n                <!-- Point 3 -->\n                <div class=\"bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl border border-slate-100 shadow-xl shadow-slate-200/30\">\n                    <div class=\"w-10 h-10 rounded bg-blue-50 flex items-center justify-center mb-6\">\n                        <span class=\"text-blue-600 font-bold\">03</span>\n                    </div>\n                    <h4 class=\"text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3\">Confidentiality &amp; Control</h4>\n                    <p class=\"text-slate-500 text-sm leading-relaxed\">\n                        Mediation keeps your family's private matters out of the public record. More importantly, it keeps the power of decision-making in your hands, rather than surrendering your future to a judge.\n                    </p>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>"
    },
    {
      "type": "custom_html",
      "html": "<section class=\"py-24 bg-white border-b border-slate-100\">\n        <div class=\"max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 text-center\">\n            <h2 class=\"text-3xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-6\">Ready to move forward?</h2>\n            <p class=\"text-lg text-slate-600 mb-10\">\n                Explore our availability and secure a date for your mediation session online. We offer both half-day and full-day formats to accommodate your specific needs.\n            </p>\n            <div class=\"flex flex-col sm:flex-row justify-center items-center gap-4\">\n                <a href=\"/#calendar\" class=\"inline-flex items-center justify-center px-8 py-4 text-base font-medium text-white bg-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-700 rounded-full shadow-lg shadow-blue-600/20 hover:-translate-y-0.5 transition-all duration-300 w-full sm:w-auto\">\n                    View Mediation Calendar\n                </a>\n                <a href=\"tel:2147444440\" class=\"inline-flex items-center justify-center px-8 py-4 text-base font-medium text-slate-700 bg-slate-50 hover:bg-slate-100 border border-slate-200 rounded-full transition-all duration-300 w-full sm:w-auto\">\n                    Call 214-744-4440\n                </a>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>"
    },
